<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu kipahman hawma A hung tieng,
 Sun ahim, zan ahim in;
 Thaumei guotsa leh vak san ei mu dem?
 Ginum a Amah ngakin.

[V2]
 Aw &quot;Kiguo zo&quot; I ti thei dem, suohpih?
 Lautha In lam zuon dingin;'
 Ei amah ngak zingin ei hung mu dem?
 Ngakin Lalpa hungtieng ei mu dem?

[V3]
 2. Zingkal matak, phalvaka A hunga,
 Khat khata ei hun sapa;
 I thilvawphaw Lalpa I piekdawk tieng,
 &quot;Bawl pha&quot; ti'n ahun dawng dem?

[V4]
 3. A deih bangin I na takkhan nau em?
 Hattawp in I sem nau em?
 I lungthima I ki mawhsak loh leh,.
 Chawlhna lopi chang taitiu.

[V5]
 4. Lalpa'n kigingsa a muhte hampha,
 A lopina chang tan au;
 Zing a him zankhang ahim in hung leh,
 Kigingsa'n ei hung mu dem?</lyrics>
<title>WILL JESUS FIND US WATCHING?</title>
</song>